    {
      "parameters": {
        "assignments": {
          "assignments": [
            {
              "id": "40da83ae-fd6f-4368-839e-388c063e592c",
              "name": "Prompt",
              "value": "=You are an expert in analysing Students food review. Analyse the ratings received from students for yesterdays mess menu below and provide:\n\n1. Which meal had better reviews and the possible reasons of people liking it.\n2. What performed bad and why people disliked.\n3. A summmary starting with today's date \n(the summary will also be saved in the sheets later and you will receive the summary next day for good pattern recognitaion.)\n4. How mess menu can be improved and suggest food items students will like.\nDate : {{ $json.Date }}\nPrevious Summary : {{ $json.Summary }}\nBreakfast food:\n{{ $json.Breakfast }}\nBreakfast Rating :\n{{ $json.BRating }}\nLunch food : {{ $json.Lunch }}\nLunch Rating : {{ $json.LRating }}\nDinner food : {{ $json.Dinner}}\nDinner rating : {{ $json.DRating }}\nRespond ONLY with a raw JSON object using exactly these keys:\n{\n  \"TopMeal\": <string>,\n  \"BadMeal\": <string>,\n  \"Summary\": \"<2 sentence summary>\"\n  \"FoodSuggestion\": \"<2 sentence summary>\"\n}\nNo markdown. No code fences. Start with { and end with }.",
              "type": "string"
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.set",
      "typeVersion": 3.4,
      "position": [
        768,
        -144
      ],
      "id": "e95c7880-ba12-4f72-88e7-a961cdbe959c",
      "name": "Edit Fields"
    },
